          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
            <li>Product availability, pricing, or specifications</li>
            <li>Fitness for your particular purpose or needs</li>
            <li>Results or outcomes from using recommended products</li>
            <li>Compatibility with your individual circumstances</li>
          </ul>
          <p>
            You acknowledge that using products and services mentioned on our Site is at your own risk. Always consult with qualified professionals when making decisions about health, skincare, or other personal matters.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-off-white">Affiliate Relationships</h2>
          <p>
            SwankyBoyz participates in affiliate marketing programs. Some links on our Site are affiliate links, meaning we may earn a commission when you make a purchase through these links at no additional cost to you.
          </p>
          <p>
            Our affiliate relationships never influence our editorial recommendations. See our <a href="/affiliate-disclosure" class="text-champagne hover:text-champagne/80 transition underline">Affiliate Disclosure</a> for complete details.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-off-white">Intellectual Property</h2>
          <p>
            All content on SwankyBoyz, including text, graphics, logos, images, and software, is the property of SwankyBoyz or its content suppliers and is protected by international copyright laws.
          </p>
          <p>
            You may not reproduce, distribute, modify, or create derivative works from any content on our Site without express written permission from SwankyBoyz.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-off-white">User Conduct</h2>
          <p>When using our Site, you agree not to:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
            <li>Violate any applicable laws or regulations</li>
            <li>Infringe on intellectual property rights</li>
            <li>Transmit harmful code, viruses, or malicious software</li>
            <li>Attempt to gain unauthorized access to our systems</li>
            <li>Use automated systems to access our Site without permission</li>
            <li>Harass, abuse, or harm other users</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-off-white">Product Links and Pricing</h2>
          <p>
            Product prices and availability displayed on our Site are subject to change without notice. We are not responsible for pricing errors or discrepancies. Always verify current prices and availability on the merchant's website before making a purchase.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-off-white">Third-Party Links</h2>
          <p>
            Our Site may contain links to third-party websites. We are not responsible for the content, privacy practices, or terms of service of these external sites. Accessing third-party links is at your own risk.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-off-white">Disclaimer of Warranties</h2>
          <p>
            The Site and all content are provided "as is" without warranties of any kind, either express or implied. SwankyBoyz disclaims all warranties, including but not limited to:
